        {
            "parameters": {
                "content": "## Breakpoint customer support demo\n\nFlow:\nGoogle Sheets \u2192 OpenAI risky reply \u2192 Breakpoint outbound inspection \u2192 Google Sheets before/after update.\n\nBefore running:\n1. Upload/import the spreadsheet into Google Sheets.\n2. Replace PASTE_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID_HERE in both Google Sheets nodes.\n3. Add Google Sheets credentials.\n4. Replace PASTE_OPENAI_API_KEY_HERE.\n5. Replace PASTE_BREAKPOINT_API_KEY_HERE.\n\nYour app already sends Slack notifications on each inspection, so this workflow does not need a Slack node.",
                "height": 360,
                "width": 420
            },
            "id": "1b2b4f0b-0d0a-4c64-b16e-1a9d6a4c0009",
            "name": "Setup Notes",
